name: Vitro Portrait No. 1
description: Great are the times when we are filled with creativity and inspiration, then wonderful works emerge from us, and so this is how that time has come for me. Now I can expose to you part of my creativity, being this work the first one to show to the world of nfts. Although I made it in a past time, with very different emotions than today, I decided to retouch it in some parts, because it didn't look symmetrical enough to me, and there were some pixels out of place. I hope you like it!
